              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-light mt-2 text-center">--color-accent-dark</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-light text-center">深橘（Hover）</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <Alert color="warning" title="💡 為什麼選橘色？">
            <ul class="space-y-1 ml-5 list-disc">
              <li>與 Teal (#00aaaa) 形成強烈視覺對比（互補色）</li>
